{UPTOWN SPRINGDALE}

Natsuki: “Oh, my gosh…I honestly feel bad for Jibanyan. Is he always this aggressive towards trucks, Nate?”

Nate: “Yeah, Jibanyan has a bit of a truck problem. The moment he sees one come by, he just goes HAM on them - striking with all his might. It’s actually a bit of…trauma from back before he became a Yo-kai.”
